      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, dependable ride? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers solid everyday transportation at a great price! The exterior shows visible signs of use \u2014 expect some scratches and minor blemishes consistent with its age and mileage. The interior has noticeable wear but remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, it gets the job done, making it a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers who want reliable wheels without breaking the bank. Come take it for a spin!",
