    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable, Well-Maintained & Ready for the Road \u2014 A Smart Buy! This solid used car is in good condition and makes a fantastic everyday driver. The exterior shows some light wear and minor surface scratches consistent with normal use, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all the essentials in good working order. Under the hood, this car runs reliably and handles daily driving with ease. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle at a fair price, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,500, a price that honestly reflects its mint overall condition. The exterior is in exceptional shape \u2014 paint is vibrant and glossy with no visible scratches, chips, or fading, and the body panels are straight and clean. The interior is equally impressive, showing virtually no signs of wear; upholstery, trim, and all surfaces look fresh and well-maintained. Mechanically, the car performs as expected from a well-cared-for vehicle in top-tier condition \u2014 all systems function properly, and there are no known issues to disclose. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been genuinely kept in outstanding condition from top to bottom.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Great Condition Gem \u2014 Reliable, Clean, and Ready to Go!** This is a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle that's been well taken care of! This car is in good condition \u2014 the paint shows only minor signs of everyday wear, the interior is clean and comfortable, and mechanically it's running strong. It's not a show car, but it's far from a project \u2014 this is a dependable, solid vehicle you can trust for daily driving or weekend adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior has noticeable scratches, scuffs, and areas of paint wear. The interior shows clear signs of use, including worn upholstery and some minor damage to trim pieces. Mechanically the car runs and drives, though it has not been recently serviced and may require some attention.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in fair shape and represents a functional, budget-conscious option for a used car buyer. The car shows more than typical wear for its age, including visible cosmetic imperfections such as scratches, minor dents, and interior wear that goes beyond the norm. Mechanically, the vehicle runs and drives, but prospective buyers should be prepared for the possibility that some components may need attention or servicing in the near term. It is not a showroom-quality vehicle, but it is a legitimate daily driver for someone willing to invest some time and modest money into upkeep. A pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly encouraged. This is an honest listing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the car's actual condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is priced to reflect that reality \u2014 it is sold strictly as-is and is best suited for buyers who are comfortable taking on a project car, need a parts donor, or simply require bare-bones transportation with the understanding that repairs will be needed. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable dents, scratches, and rust in multiple areas. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and may not be fully reliable for daily driving without attention from a qualified mechanic. There are also interior deficiencies \u2014 worn seating, damaged trim, and possible non-functional features. We are not representing this car as road-ready or dependable in its current state. If you are a hands-on buyer, a mechanic, or someone looking for a low-cost entry point willing to invest time and money, this could be the right opportunity \u2014 but please come with realistic expectations. No warranty is offered, and all sales are final.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    }
